de.fhg.fokus.restac.httpx.core.dispatcher
Interface HTTPXActionMessageDispatcher

All Known Implementing Classes:
HTTPXActionMessageDispatcherImpl, HTTPXManagedActionMessageDispatcher, TCPClientManagedActionMessageDispatcher, TCPServerManagedActionMessageDispatcher, UDPMUManagedActionMessageDispatcher, UDPUManagedActionMessageDispatcher
public interface HTTPXActionMessageDispatcher

The Interface defines methods to deliver synchronous, asynchronous and plain messages (e.g. UDP unicast/multicast ).

Author:
Murat Ates
